title: Sasha Sessions: A Team USA Podcast Preview
itunes:title: Sasha Sessions: A Team USA Podcast Preview
description: Sasha Cohen, Olympic silver medalist in figure skating, hosts Team USA's first ever podcast. Sasha speaks with exceptional people - both athletes and thought leaders - about their struggles, motivations and quest to define who they are in the world. Subscribe wherever you get your podcasts, and join Sasha for new episodes every Monday.
author: U.S. Olympic & Paralympic Committee
